# Feature delivery rules

Before building any feature:
1. Read ai/FIELD_NAMES.md — use exact field names
2. Check if the pattern already exists (e.g. dream.tsx for a new feature screen)
3. Follow the existing pattern — do not invent new component patterns
4. All text goes through i18n — no hardcoded strings
5. Every feature must handle: loading state, error state, empty state, retry

Route registration: add new routes BEFORE wildcards in app.ts.
Check position: grep -n "app\.route\|app\.use\|\*" astro-coach-api/src/app.ts
